    // Link: https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/0320a718e8e07b1d932f5acb8ad9cec9d9eed99b/contracts/utils/math/SignedMath.sol#L37-L42
    /// @notice get the abs from a signed number
